738
00:31:26,440 --> 00:31:27,770
Patawarin mo ako sa pangungulit,

739
00:31:29,400 --> 00:31:30,720
pero hayaan mong tanungin kita nang isa pang beses:

740
00:31:30,720 --> 00:31:32,050
Talaga bang hindi tayo pupunta

741
00:31:32,590 --> 00:31:33,640
