746
00:31:40,440 --> 00:31:42,510
Kahit
hindi siya iniimbestigahan ni Wang Xuanfan,

747
00:31:42,510 --> 00:31:44,310
Ako pa rin ang magpaparusa sa kanya.

748
00:31:46,510 --> 00:31:47,040
Sige.

749
00:31:47,920 --> 00:31:49,380
Susundin ko ang iyong pangunguna at

750
00:31:49,510 --> 00:31:51,970
