753
00:31:59,680 --> 00:32:01,550
Tiyak na nakita ng Kanyang Kamahalan ang bantayog.

754
00:32:01,550 --> 00:32:03,480
Jiuheng, pumunta ka agad sa palasyo.

755
00:32:16,960 --> 00:32:17,550
Mahal kong Ginang.

756
00:32:20,480 --> 00:32:21,070
Mahal kong Ginang.

757
00:32:25,030 --> 00:32:25,720
Mahal kong Ginang.

