776
00:33:14,270 --> 00:33:15,310
Kalokohan!

777
00:33:17,960 --> 00:33:18,760
Kamahalan,

778
00:33:19,030 --> 00:33:19,720
noong panahong iyon, mayroon akong

779
00:33:19,720 --> 00:33:21,640
