784
00:33:28,440 --> 00:33:31,170
Hindi nag-iimbento
lang si Lord Zhang ng mga bagay-bagay.

785
00:33:32,070 --> 00:33:32,870
Chen Jiuheng.

786
00:33:36,310 --> 00:33:37,220
Kamahalan,

787
00:33:37,510 --> 00:33:39,210
May alam ako

788
00:33:39,350 --> 00:33:40,350
na maaaring patunayan na

789
00:33:40,350 --> 00:33:42,070
ang yumaong Prinsipe Chengqing at Panginoong Wang

790
