821
00:34:38,400 --> 00:34:40,199
Ang buong pamilya niya ay pinatay.

822
00:34:40,590 --> 00:34:43,190
Ngunit si Panginoong Wang ay namuhay nang mapayapa,

823
00:34:43,400 --> 00:34:44,400
at mayroon pa ngang

824
00:34:45,320 --> 00:34:46,760
