825
00:34:46,760 --> 00:34:47,710
Kalokohan!

826
00:34:48,320 --> 00:34:49,120
Kamahalan,

827
00:34:49,550 --> 00:34:50,440
Kinukulit ako ni Chen Yanyun

828
00:34:50,440 --> 00:34:52,040
