849
00:35:25,280 --> 00:35:27,000
at naghihintay ng parusa

850
00:35:27,360 --> 00:35:28,800
hanggang sa Tatlong Tanggapan ng Hukuman

851
00:35:28,800 --> 00:35:30,530
