873
00:37:10,800 --> 00:37:11,600
Ikatlong Guro.

874
00:37:12,360 --> 00:37:13,160
Umuwi na tayo.

875
00:37:13,510 --> 00:37:15,230
Dinakip
ng Court of Judicial Review si Gu Deyuan.

876
00:37:15,230 --> 00:37:15,960
Ang pamilyang Gu

877
00:37:16,030 --> 00:37:17,670
